# 📅 Scheduling Platform

A modern, fully customizable scheduling platform designed for teams, professionals, and organizations.  
Easily manage bookings, automate workflows, and integrate with your favorite tools.

---

## 🚀 Features Overview

### 🕒 Core Scheduling

- Multiple event types  
- Custom durations (15, 30, 60, 90 min, custom)  
- Collective and group events  
- Round-robin scheduling  
- One-off meetings  
- Buffer times (before/after events)  
- Daily event limits  
- Timezone detection & conversion  
- Custom office hours and per-day availability  
- Seasonal schedules & holiday blocking  

---

### 🎟️ Booking Experience

- Real-time availability display  
- Smart time slot suggestions  
- Custom booking forms  
- Pre-filled invitee details  
- Multiple language support  
- Custom questions (required/optional)  
- Location options: in-person, phone, video  
- Automatic video conferencing links  
- Payment collection (Stripe integration)  
- Multi-currency and tax calculation support  

---

### 📆 Calendar Integration

- Google Calendar sync  
- Outlook / Office 365 sync  
- iCloud calendar sync  
- Real-time conflict detection  
- Automatic updates and two-way sync  
- Multi-calendar management  
- Permission-based access control  

---

### 🔔 Notifications & Reminders

- Email confirmations  
- SMS reminders  
- Custom reminder intervals  
- Host and invitee notifications  
- Follow-up emails  
- No-show alerts  
- Cancellation and rescheduling notices  

---

### 👥 Team Features

- Multi-member team support  
- Team availability overlay  
- Per-member event types  
- Round-robin and routing logic  
- Collective availability  
- Team performance analytics  
- Admin-level team management  

---

### 🎨 Customization & Branding

- Custom domains and subdomains  
- Brand colors, logos, and favicon  
- Custom email templates  
- White-label options  
- Remove platform branding  
- Custom confirmation and cancellation pages  
- Full CSS customization  

---

### 🔗 Embed Options

- Inline embeds  
- Pop-up widgets  
- Dedicated landing pages  
- Direct booking links  
- Pre-populated forms  
- Mobile-optimized embeds  
- WordPress and Squarespace integration  

---

### ⚙️ Workflow Automation

- Zapier integration  
- Webhooks and API access  
- Custom workflow triggers  
- Conditional logic  
- Geographic, language, and answer-based routing  

---

### 📊 Analytics & Reporting

- Meeting volume and time slot analytics  
- Busiest day insights  
- No-show tracking  
- Revenue tracking  
- Team performance metrics  
- Invitee analytics  
- Exportable reports and custom date ranges  

---

### 🔌 Integrations

- Zoom, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams  
- GoToMeeting, Webex  
- Salesforce, HubSpot, Slack, Intercom  
- Stripe, PayPal  
- Google Analytics  

---

### 🔐 Security & Admin

- Password & CAPTCHA protection  
- GDPR compliance  
- End-to-end data encryption  
- Single Sign-On (SSO) integration  
- User management and permission levels  
- Audit logs and data export  
- Account recovery  

---
